description:
Maeda Keiji is a wandering samurai who hates men. She is a master of Qi, a master of disguise and also wields an umbrella in battle. As a childhood friend of Kanetsugu, Keiji has taken her appearance to initially teach the girls how to use Qi. She likes to touch other girls breasts to compare their size and to determine who has the greatest. Her method of choice for long-distance transport is by motorcycle. She was nicknamed "Maedake" by Jubei.
Source: Wiki
name: Maeda Keiji
